> Commander Yash floats beyond the airlock. The Earth turns below, impossibly blue.
[caption bg:#000000 color:#aaddff pos:top-left] She had been up here for 312 days.
[caption bg:#000000 color:#aaddff pos:top-left] The last transmission came on day 301.
[caption bg:#000000 color:#ffffff pos:bottom-right] She decided to come home anyway.